'''第26屆[[哥譚獨立電影獎|哥譚獨立電影獎]]'''（{{lang-en|'''The 26th Annual Gotham Independent Film Awards'''}}）是於2016年11月28日正式舉行的電影獎項，入圍名單於2016年10月20日公布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/gotham-awards-nominations-2016-list-nominees-1201895205/?platform=hootsuite|title=Gotham Awards Nominations 2016: ‘Manchester By The Sea’ Leads with Four|last=Cox|first=Gordon|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=October 20, 2016|accessdate=October 20, 2016|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403040554/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/gotham-awards-nominations-2016-list-nominees-1201895205/?platform=hootsuite|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演員[[伊森·霍克|伊森·霍克]]、[[艾美·亞當斯|艾美·亞當斯]]、導演[[奧利佛·史東|奧利佛·史東]]與製片人[[艾農·米爾臣|艾農·米爾臣]]獲在儀式上受頒職業貢獻獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/09/gotham-awards-2016-amy-adams-ethan-hawke-actor-tribute-oliver-stone-director-ifp-1201723919/|title=Amy Adams And Ethan Hawke To Receive Actor Tributes|date=September 7, 2016|accessdate=October 20, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021063859/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/09/gotham-awards-2016-amy-adams-ethan-hawke-actor-tribute-oliver-stone-director-ifp-1201723919/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://filmmakermagazine.com/99942-arnon-milchan-to-receive-industry-tribute-at-2016-gotham-independent-film-awards/|title=Arnon Milchan to Receive Industry Tribute at 2016 Gotham Independent Film Awards|date=September 22, 2016|accessdate=October 20, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114113701/http://filmmakermagazine.com/99942-arnon-milchan-to-receive-industry-tribute-at-2016-gotham-independent-film-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

